1
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:08,222
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,350 --> 00:01:11,262
=Episode 10=

3
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:13,680
(Has Xu Yu calmed down?)

4
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,599
(This time, I broke her heart.)

5
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:19,120
(She definitely
won't forgive me easily.)

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,599
Your Majesty.

7
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:24,640
The night is chilly.
Please go back to rest.

8
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,280
No need.

9
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,000
I don't need you here.
You may leave now.

10
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,040
Yes.

11
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:37,540
Xu...

12
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,400
Lady Tao.

13
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,680
How did you escape?

14
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,239
That's none of your concern.

15
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,120
Xu Yu.

16
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,319
I'll kill you
to avenge my child's death.

17
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:56,519
The one who killed your child
was his own father.

18
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:58,519
What nonsense!

19
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,079
His Majesty has already told me.

20
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,359
That night, you got him drunk

21
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,640
and then faked the consummation.

22
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,599
In fact, you already
had someone else's baby.

23
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,840
You would pass your child off
as imperial heir.

24
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:14,520
So he might one day inherit the throne.

25
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,560
Am I right or not?

26
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,080
Impossible!

27
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,520
If Xiao Jinyun had known,

28
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,560
- he wouldn't...
- Even if he knew,

29
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:25,759
he never intended
to harm an innocent child.

30
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,599
What about you?

31
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,439
Just for a man,

32
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,479
you actually ruined your own reputation

33
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:33,000
and made your own child a pawn.

34
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:35,199
Nonsense!

35
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,879
I didn't!

36
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,520
I never did!

37
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,800
I loved my child deeply.

38
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:45,240
I loved my child.

39
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:45,960
Really?

40
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,240
If you truly loved your child,

41
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,439
would you let him die a tragic death

42
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,919
to shield the true murderer?

43
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,360
Xu Yu.

44
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,840
Are you trying to hear the truth?

45
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,319
Are you?

46
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:07,240
I'll tell you everything
when you're dead.

47
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,120
Guards!

48
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,120
Help!

49
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,319
Guards!

50
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:31,960
Your Majesty!

51
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,580
Your Majesty, an emergency!

52
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,280
A message from the Fengyi Palace.

53
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,919
Lady Tao escaped the dungeon

54
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,479
and attempted to kill Her Majesty.

55
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,479
Xu Yu.

56
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,719
- I'm sorry.
- I'm sorry.

57
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,159
Let me speak first.

58
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,039
It's all because I'm too weak,

59
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,719
always letting your body get injured.

60
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,000
What about you?

61
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,319
Were you frightened
by Lady Tao's assassination?

62
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,879
I am the Emperor.

63
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:12,680
I've witnessed many such bloody scenes.

64
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,479
Now I suspect

65
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,959
Lady Tao deliberately sought death.

66
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,519
If those behind her

67
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,160
wanted to silence her,

68
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,639
it proves she truly had accomplices.

69
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:25,920
So,

70
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,480
she failed to kill me
and then killed herself.

71
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,480
It eventually became a harem fight.

72
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,040
But now that Lady Tao is dead,

73
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,680
we can't connect the dots then.

74
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:41,959
I just fear you'll face danger again.

75
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,279
Xu Yu.

76
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,160
Are you worried about me?

77
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,240
Yes.

78
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,319
I am worried about you.

79
00:04:58,079 --> 00:05:01,079
Moreover, I wrongly accused you.

80
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:06,480
I've reflected for long
on the incense poisoning incident.

81
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,199
I realized

82
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,959
your concern for me wasn't feigned.

83
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:14,120
Now you guard my body for me

84
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,040
and endure the same pain as I do.

85
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,480
Had you known earlier,

86
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,120
you'd never have let me suffer this.

87
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,680
Xu Yu.

88
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:23,519
Believe it or not,

89
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:26,720
I'd rather hurt myself than hurt you.

90
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,240
Actually, you were right before.

91
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,079
I am just a feeble man.

92
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:35,759
All I can do is talking.
I'm utterly useless to you.

93
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,800
Wait, when did I ever say that?

94
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,839
(One year ago)
You have no idea about him.

95
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,399
He is so weak.

96
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:50,959
One slap from me would knock him flat.

97
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:54,759
He always gives me a lecture.

98
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,240
If he's so capable,
he can just spar with me.

99
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:05,160
I was referring to my tutor.

100
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,439
And that's why

101
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:08,040
you gave me the cold shoulder.

102
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:10,319
You also deliberately
promoted Zhao Qiluo.

103
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,959
Soon after, I calmed down.

104
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:18,600
And I went to find you.

105
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,639
But you locked your palace gates.

106
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,839
You even told your maids

107
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,240
that anyone could enter except me.

108
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,639
It made me so furious
that I reviewed memorials all night!

109
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:31,079
Then our mutual aversion
over the past year

110
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:34,399
was all caused
by small misunderstandings.

111
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,319
Xu Yu.

112
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,160
Listen to me.

113
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,480
It's all my fault.

114
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,680
My bad.

115
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,360
I neglected you

116
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,879
and deliberately provoked you.

117
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:50,079
That's what drove us further apart.

118
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:58,279
Stay away from my chest before speaking.

119
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:58,779
Listen.

120
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,800
Promise me.

121
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:04,240
From now on,
we must be honest with each other,

122
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:07,560
and never let such misunderstandings
damage our relationship again.

123
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,759
I do care about you.

124
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:11,279
I did misunderstand you.

125
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,319
I failed to understand your thoughts,

126
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:17,279
indeed.

127
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,879
I also made mistakes.

128
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,279
If I hadn't been so stubborn,

129
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,040
I wouldn't have misunderstood you
that much.

130
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,199
Xiao Jinyun.

131
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,680
I'm sorry.

132
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:35,720
Xu Yu.

133
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,879
Let's give each other another chance

134
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,639
to grow closer, okay?

135
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:46,688
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

136
00:07:46,784 --> 00:07:51,447
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

137
00:07:51,968 --> 00:07:54,144
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

138
00:07:54,144 --> 00:07:58,022
♪This life is but a solitary boat♪

139
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,879
Come on.

140
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,800
At this moment,
you should close your eyes.

141
00:08:12,448 --> 00:08:14,688
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

142
00:08:14,688 --> 00:08:18,619
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

143
00:08:18,990 --> 00:08:24,109
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

144
00:08:24,109 --> 00:08:26,368
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

145
00:08:26,368 --> 00:08:29,792
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

146
00:08:29,792 --> 00:08:35,937
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

147
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,320
(From now on,)

148
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,159
(I will never let go of your hand.)

149
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,600
Your Majesty.

150
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,200
Urgent military news from the northwest.

151
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:05,000
Dada and Houyi have invaded our borders.

152
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,440
We have lost two consecutive battles

153
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,799
and retreated to Jiayu Pass.

154
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,919
General Xu is recuperating
in the capital.

155
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,519
Marshal Xu can't
resist the invasion alone!

156
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:22,799
Dada invaded before.

157
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:26,360
I suspect
Marshal Xu is too old to fight.

158
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:29,080
I propose replacing him,

159
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:32,559
disbanding his soldiers,
and redistributing them.

160
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:36,320
This is utter nonsense!

161
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,600
Changing commanders mid-campaign
is disastrous!

162
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,720
(He clearly aims
to strip Father of his military power)

163
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:44,160
(and disband the Xu Army)

164
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,879
(to reduce the forces opposing him.)

165
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,399
I volunteer for battle.

166
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:55,159
(These generals excessively revere
and trust Father.)

167
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:58,759
(No wonder Jinyun and his mother
are wary of my family.)

168
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:03,200
The northwestern front is critical.

169
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:05,480
But capital defense is equally vital.

170
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,600
General Chen, no further debate.

171
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,080
I already have someone

172
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,960
in mind.

173
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,919
Ministries of War and Revenue,
draft plans.

174
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,559
Reinforce the northwest
with troops and supplies.

175
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,639
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

176
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,120
No way!

177
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,120
Why not?

178
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,240
I'm Marshal Xu's daughter.

179
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,240
I can do it.

180
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,080
Xu Yu.

181
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,200
Don't act on impulse.

182
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,399
Are there no candidates beyond you?

183
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:37,159
Our soldiers either die on battlefields,

184
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:39,240
or get framed and crippled,

185
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:42,720
or starve on the front lines
due to supply shortages.

186
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,559
Supply shortages?

187
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,720
Why was I never informed?

188
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:48,960
Military officers are clumsy.

189
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,592
Civil officials never report it.

190
00:10:53,984 --> 00:10:55,320
In the past,

191
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,639
I indeed made some mistakes.

192
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,360
Your Majesty.

193
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:04,000
A capable general is rare.

194
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,600
Now that we've switched bodies,

195
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,240
let me lead the troops into battle.

196
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,120
I believe I can achieve victory.

197
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:13,240
I cannot bear to let you endure
hardships or distant campaigns.

198
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,519
Moreover,
battlefields are full of dangers.

199
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:17,240
How can I risk your life?

200
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,159
I must go.

201
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,480
The longer the war drags on,

202
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,840
the weaker the morale becomes.

203
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:28,440
The rumor of Chen's weakness
has circulated for decades.

204
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:32,279
That's why Dada and Houyi
have been wantonly harassing us.

205
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,159
Your Majesty.

206
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:39,080
My military ability is as good as
that of my father and my brother.

207
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,320
Please let me go.

208
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,919
I'm confident I can win.

209
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:54,399
But there's no crown prince currently.

210
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:55,840
Who will run the state?

211
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:01,759
I have someone.

212
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,000
Xu Yu intends to go to war.

213
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:09,720
She asked me to run the nation.

214
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,240
And Jinyun actually agreed.

215
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,320
They must be insane.

216
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,759
They did the right thing.

217
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:18,759
I can't believe this.

218
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,039
I do not agree.

219
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:21,519
Your Majesty.

220
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:23,519
You've only held power for a few years.

221
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:25,440
Countless eyes in the capital
are on you.

222
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,639
The slightest misstep from you

223
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,799
will bring catastrophic consequences,

224
00:12:30,159 --> 00:12:31,720
let alone going to war.

225
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,399
You don't know archery

226
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:34,320
or martial skills.

227
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,559
How can you fight?

228
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,480
Mother.

229
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,519
I always remember

230
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,960
how Chen was founded.

231
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:43,960
My great-grandfather
and father built it.

232
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:46,240
They fought on horseback
for nearly a century.

233
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,120
Countless men died on the battlefields.

234
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,279
And countless men joined the army.

235
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:51,799
Women and children became homeless.

236
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,320
Now I'm currently ruling the nation.

237
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:58,960
I can't see our borders get raided

238
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,759
and people there suffer anymore.

239
00:13:09,639 --> 00:13:10,200
Mother.

240
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,152
His Majesty advocates civil governance.

241
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,799
But the borders have suffered from war
for too long.

242
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,879
His Majesty's intention
is to tell our people

243
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,200
that they're on His Majesty's land.

244
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:26,159
They deserve their emperor's protection.

245
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,399
It's also to warn invading enemies

246
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:32,159
that every emperor of Chen
grows up on horseback.

247
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:42,112
Mother. I have practiced riding
and archery with Xu Yu

248
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:45,240
precisely to reclaim our lost land
one day

249
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,639
and restore our might.

250
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,639
I intend to lead our troops
and display Chen's power.

251
00:13:50,159 --> 00:13:52,879
We'll secure ten years of peace
for the northern border.

252
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:55,799
Very well.

253
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:58,840
Our family has never
had a cowardly emperor!

254
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:01,080
Your Majesty, go ahead.

255
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:03,960
Thank you, Mother.

256
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,960
(Xu Yu,)

257
00:14:11,399 --> 00:14:14,000
(I don't know
how you make my son obsessed with you.)

258
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,320
(Perhaps it's not bad.)

259
00:14:15,879 --> 00:14:18,720
(At least he hasn't lost his ambition.)

260
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,399
Mother.

261
00:14:23,159 --> 00:14:26,639
Many officials resent the Xu family.

262
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:31,080
I fear they'll target Xu Yu
while I'm away.

263
00:14:31,799 --> 00:14:34,039
Rest assured, I will handle everything.

264
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:38,879
I also hope that Xu Yu won't get hurt
under any circumstances.

265
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:43,639
Whatever happens,
await my return for final judgment.

266
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:46,320
If it can let you campaign
with peace of mind,

267
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:49,120
I can certainly promise you.

268
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,000
Thank you, Mother.

269
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:53,639
Thank you, Mother.

270
00:15:15,008 --> 00:15:20,192
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

271
00:15:20,928 --> 00:15:25,491
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

272
00:15:26,816 --> 00:15:32,231
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

273
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:37,344
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

274
00:15:37,984 --> 00:15:43,248
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

275
00:15:43,616 --> 00:15:49,293
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

276
00:15:49,632 --> 00:15:51,648
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

277
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:55,584
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

278
00:15:56,160 --> 00:16:00,832
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

279
00:16:01,376 --> 00:16:03,136
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

280
00:16:03,456 --> 00:16:07,072
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

281
00:16:07,319 --> 00:16:12,846
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
